Package data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ITaskData
    Facade for TaskData - used by the managers for read/write operations to TaskData.
    ITaskDataFileInputOutput
    Facade for TaskData - used by FileInputOutput to synchronise TaskData with an external file.
    ITaskDataUndo
    Facade for TaskData - used by the undoManager to retrieve undo snapshots.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoCompleteDictionary
    A dictionary that keeps an updated list of strings that can be auto-completed.
    EuclideanAlgorithm
    Not actually used in the program.
    Task
    The Task object that is stored in the TaskData class.
    TaskData
    Program memory for the tasks in the program.
    It is the job of TaskData to ensure that the absolute index of each task
    remains the same even after deletion / addition of tasks.
    TaskId
    Absolute ID of a task.
    Immutable
    UndoSnapshot
    A "Snapshot" container holding all the UndoTaskSnapshots after an action has been executed.
    UndoTaskSnapshot
    Immutable.
